&lt;p&gt;To change color schema, add your custom css in backend, on how to add custom css please refer to &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.omind.org/docs/custom-css/&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. The CSS may be one of bellow, or you can edit youself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;White&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;a, a:visited{color:#0088cc;}
a:hover{color:#0088cc;}
header{background: #ffffff;}
header a{color:#000000;}
nav li a, nav li a:visited{color:#ffffff;}
nav li a:hover, nav li.current a{color:#d8d8d8;}
#logo{color:#333333;}&lt;/pre&gt;
